CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 24, 1957, pg. A12 reads: "Intriguing Trio at Dr. James Hopson's musicale in Pittsburgh included Tony Taylor of Washington, Pa.; Anne Goode Carroll, Chicago, and Charles Danforth, Cleveland. - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Tony Taylor, Anne Goode Carroll, and Charles Danforth, gathered for cocktail party in home of Nathaniel and Helen Dandridge
